        "layout": "left",
        "title": "Gardening Intern",
        "text": "<p>Roll up your sleeves and help bring our gardens to life. As a Gardening Intern, you’ll dig, plant, weed, water, and harvest in our vegetable beds and flower rows—learning as you grow. We’ll teach you the basics of organic, sustainable gardening while you get your hands dirty in the best way. Whether you're prepping beds for tomatoes or cutting wildflowers for the Farmstand, your work helps feed our community and keep the farm blooming. No experience necessary—just a good attitude and a love for being outside.</p>",
