        "text": "<p>If working outdoors with the hum of bees and the smell of fresh mulch sounds like your kind of day, this one’s for you. As a landscaping volunteer, you’ll help us shape and care for the land—mowing fields, spreading mulch, trimming back overgrowth, clearing trails, and helping with seasonal projects that keep the farm looking its best. This is honest, physical work that makes a real impact and gives you a front-row seat to the changing seasons.</p>",
